SUBROUTINE WeHaveAWinner
 T
 T Congratulations.  Your final score was @Score  out of 113 possible points.
* Should we show a victory pic here?
 EQU Temp 1
 CALL Victory
 WIN
ENDSUB
*
*
*
SUBROUTINE Victory   * Recursively play a victory swoop!
 NOTE Temp 1
 ADD Temp 15
 IF Temp < 520 THEN
  CALL Victory
 ENDIF
ENDSUB
*
*
*
SUBROUTINE BuyTheFarm
 T
 T You have died.  Your final score was @Score  out of 113 possible points.
 SHOW Death
 EQU Temp 500
 CALL BoughtIt
 DIE
ENDSUB
*
*
*
SUBROUTINE BoughtIt  * Recursively play a death swoop down
 NOTE Temp 1
 SUB Temp 15
 IF Temp > 16 THEN
  CALL BoughtIt
 ENDIF
ENDSUB
*
*
*
SUBROUTINE SwimAcross
 EQU CrossedWater 1
 EQU InConnTunn 1
 GO Connecting_Tunnel
ENDSUB
*
* ----- END OF FILE
